<p style="text-align:left;"><strong><u>How to Opt-Out of Data Collection, Use or Disclosure</u></strong><br>In addition to the method(s) described in the <em>How to Access, Modify, Delete, or Challenge the Data Collected</em> section, we provide the following specific opt-out methods for the forms of collection, use, or disclosure of your personal data:
