<p style="text-align:left;"><strong><u>Cookie Policy</u></strong><br>A cookie is a small file, stored on a user's hard drive by a website. Its purpose is to collect data relating to the user's browsing habits. You can choose to be notified each time a cookie is transmitted. You can also choose to disable cookies entirely in your internet browser, but this may decrease the quality of your user experience.
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">We use the following types of cookies on our Site:
</p>
<ol start="1">
